Marie Osborne Yeats https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie_Osborne_Yeats 0 Marie Osborne Yeats (November 5, 1911 – November 11, 2010) was the first major child star of American silent films. She was usually billed simply as Baby Marie. Marie_Osborne_Yeats ( November_5_,_1911 – November_11_,_2010 ) was the_first_major_child_star of American_silent_films . She was_usually_billed simply as Baby_Marie .
